node.text:
On our way to a drive thru Xmas lights covid style extravaganza, my kid found his favorite persons bracelet.
Then he made an epic exit but soon realized he truly wanted the pepper he picked from the garden. I share this because it feels very important somehow.

node.text: My friend @butchwalker sent me this clip tonight that his friend Harley Ellis took at a peaceful protest in Aurora, CO for Elijah McClain. Elijah used to play violin for cats at the shelter. Now, here, Ashanti Floyd, the “mad violinist” plays in his honor. I wish Elijah could have been alive to hear it. I wish for all of us to treat each other like we are each other’s kids. The only way out of anger and heartbreak is love. There has to be a better way. The current way isn’t working for anyone. Let’s be human again. #fuckracism #blacklivesmatter
